iverser Stadtkarten. Das Buch zeigt den Zusammenhang von Stadtplanung und Politik auf und liefert über Wien hinaus neue Erkenntnisse zum Umgang mit historischer Bausubstanz.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 04. Okt 2022) 0aCity planningzAustriazViennaxHistoryy20th century. 0aUrban renewalzAustriazViennaxHistoryy20th century. 4aArchitekturgeschichte. 4aDenkmalschutz. 4aEnsembleschutz. 4aStädtebau. 7aARCHITECTURE / Historic Preservation / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2022 Part 1z978311076682008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Architecture and Design 2021z9783110753783oZDB-23-DAD08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG0 cprintz978303562379640uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783035623802zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783035623802zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783035623802/original  a978-3-11-076682-0 DG Plus DeG Package 2022 Part 1b2022  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DADb2021  aZDB-23-DGGb2021  aZDB-23-GOA